      "updated": 1784040464868,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Functional Requirements\n1.Allows 30 req/minute from same id\n2.Whatever is after will be stored in a \nDeadLetter Queue / request dropped\n(HTTP 429)\n3. Allows different parts use different\nlimiters\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Functional Requirements\n1.Allows 30 req/minute from same id\n2.Whatever is after will be stored in a \nDeadLetter Queue / request dropped (HTTP 429)\n3. Allows different parts use different limiters\n",
